// speed 1.0 >> seq 60 >> sp \smp plays once every 2 seconds
// speed 0.5 >> seq 60 >> sp \smp plays once every 4 seconds
// speed 0.5 >> seq _ _ _ 60 >> sp \dn plays at 3, 7, ... seconds

~dumdidum: imp 0.0 >> delayms 31000 >> sp \dumdidum
~noiz: noiz 42 >> delayms 51000 >> lpf 200.0 40.0 >> mul 0.2

~load: imp 0.0 >> sawsynth 0.01 2.0 >> lpf 400.0 20.0
~drum: seq 70 55 42 42 >> bd 0.1 >> mul 0.3 >> delayms 2000
~d5: speed 0.333 >> seq 60 __ __ __  60 __ __ __  60_ 60 __ __ >> sp \dum1
~d4: speed 0.333 >> seq __ 60 __ __  __ 60 __ __  _60 __ __ __ >> sp \duvum
~d3: speed 0.333 >> seq __ __ 60 __  __ __ 60 __  __  __ 60 __ >> sp \dn
~d2: speed 0.333 >> seq __ __ __ 60  __ __ __ 60  __  __ __ 60 >> sp \dum
~d1: speed 0.333 >> seq 60 __ __ __  60 __ __ __  __  __ __ __ >> sp \dumm
~ss: speed 2.0 >> seq 80_80 80 80_80 80 >> hh 0.09 >> mul 0.5
~duus: mix ~d1 ~d2 ~d3 ~d4 ~d5 ~ss >> delayms 6000
~music: mix ~drum ~duus ~dumdidum ~noiz >> plate 0.1
o: mix ~load ~music >> mul 0.9
